lead_paragraph: Jermaine Jones, Luis Solignac and Kevin Doyle scored and the Colorado Rapids won their third straight game, beating the Seattle Sounders 3-1 on Saturday night.

headline.print_headline: Jones, Solignac and Doyle Score; Rapids Beat Sounders 3-1
